        "actionType": {
          "value": "passive"
        },
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Before the hardlight havoc begins its turn in combat, it gains one of the following error states at random, losing any previous error state.</p><p><strong>Change Character</strong> The hardlight havoc regains @Damage[2d8[healing]|options:area-damage] Hit Points. </p><p><strong>Pixelation</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} from all creatures. </p><p><strong>Power Leak</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1}. At the end of its turn, it deals @Damage[4d6[electricity]|options:area-damage] damage to creatures in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save).</p><p><strong>Surge</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.nlCjDvLMf2EkV2dl]{Quickened} until the end of its turn and can use the extra action to Stride or Strike.</p>",
